                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Calculated additively with Vulkar 's headshot zoom bonus, which then calculated multiplicatively with weapon overall damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
