                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "At max level of zoom with Meticulous Aim equipped, the weapon benefits from a total of 70 + 105 = 175% headshot damage bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
                  "pageId": 1432783,
                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Despite the differing descriptions, it stacks with Target Acquired for up to 70 + 60 + 105 = 235% headshot damage bonus."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
                  "pageId": 1432783,
                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "Bodyshot damage penalty is multiplicative to weapon overall damage."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
                  "pageId": 1432783,
                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "For example, using Vulkar modded with a Serration and a maxed rank Meticulous Aim will reduce body shot damage from (225 × (1 + 1.65) = 596.25 to (225 × (1 + 1.65) × (1 - 0.45)) = 327.93 ."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
                  "pageId": 1432783,
                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "\"Bodyshot\" means anything but a headshot, including limbs or parts that might have higher damage multipliers such as MOA backpacks."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
                "provenance": {
                  "pageTitle": "Meticulous Aim",
                  "pageId": 1432783,
                  "revisionId": 2780101,
                  "section": "Notes",
                  "excerpt": "The -45% bodyshot damage is always applied twice to Slash , Heat , Toxin , and Blast , but will not apply to Electricity or Gas if they are from a headshot."
                }
              },
              {
                "reviewStatus": "draft",
